         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged in one series: I. Construction Documents, 1995; and subsequent accessions.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_2cb9d86f5394001ccad25459def563a4">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of architectural drawings, sketches, photographs, floor plans, bid addenda, and related construction and renovation records documenting the design and construction of the Irving S. Gilmore Music Library at Yale.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
